{"word":"κυματίας","slug":"κυματίας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κυματίας</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κῦμα'><el>κῦμα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>surging, billowy</i>, <el>κ. ὁ ποταμὸς ἐγένετο</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>causing waves, stormy</i>, <el>ἄνεμος</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}